content.detailedDescription:
I was on the deck of a friends house outside eating pizza with my son who is 23 and my other son who is 5 1/2 yrs old. i am 48 and my friend is in his late 60's. 
i seen the first light and thought it was strange since i knew it was not a plane since it just sat there and did not move at all. i told them to look at it and they witnessed all that i did also.
the orange orb/light glowed for a second, then a small one right next to it appeared. i call it the twin of the main one!
then there appeared 3 separate lights about a mile or so apart from each other in a straight row. they all had a twin, smaller light next to it that would appear and then vanish along with the main light.
this went on a couple of times then stopped.
about 10 minutes or so passed and the main one in the center came back out of the blue and glowed then vanished for good. we waited to see if it would appear again but it didn't.
the did not move or fly away at all. they didn't do anything but appear and then vanish a few times. they always appeared in the same spot.
my friend noticed that the light at the church flicked off during this time and pointed that out to us. the church is next to his house and can be seen from his deck also.
content.summary: Witnessed by 3 adults was 3 separate orange lights that appeared and disappeared with no trace. it was round and had a twin light next to it. one would appear, then one next to it, then one miles away to the left and right of the center one appeared

content.detailedDescription: On april 22nd, 2016 at about 1:30 pm in st. louis park, mn my co-worker and i were on a smoke break behind our building when i noticed a small black sphere, at about 215 degrees sw from our vantage, quickly ascend straight up into the sky. it appeared to be 2-3 miles away. it ascended well past 1000 ft, stopped and descended about 100 ft and stopped. it proceeded to hover there, motionless. at this point i turned to my co-worker and pointed out this strange occurrence and she had a hard time seeing the black dot in the sky. as she attempting to see it an airplane flew in the mid ground, clearly lower then the object in the sky and i told her to look straight up from the planes position. at this point the object had been hovering for about 20 seconds. she then saw it, stood up, and started to walk in the direction of the object at which point the object started moving 0 to apparent airplane speed in an instant, moving from se to nw. we moved quickly to maintain sight of the object as it passed behind a stand of trees to our immediate right. by the time we came around the trees the object was no longer visible. the whole sighting lasted a little longer than a minute. we were very excited as it looked completely unrecognizable to us. it was smaller then a plane but was perfectly spherical. it appeared as a black dot in the sky. when hovering it was completely motionless, unlike a helicopter which would move slightly when hovering. we thought it could potentially be a drone but it was well above legal flight altitudes, was much larger, and moved entirely to fast and smooth. it appeared to defy physics in its perfect standstill to immediate flight.
content.summary: Black sphere ascended, descended slightly then traveled horizontally

content.detailedDescription: I went to the lincoln memorial to take night time pictures. while standing close to the reflection pool, i took 2 long exposure pictures of the washington monument. i did not hear any sounds or notice any lights. when i got home and was reviewing the pictures, i noticed one of them had these strange lights near the monument.  i am a amateur photographer and have taken hundreds of night time shots. i know what airplane and satellite trails look like. this is not one of those. the picture is a 30 second exposure so the lights did not move or barely moved while taking the picture. there is some dust specks in the shot as evident by the blue and yellow specks. this is normal for long exposure shots. the first shot was taken 1 minute before the second shot. there are no signs of the lights in the first shot. there are 4 lights with something blurry on each end. the small dot in the middle may be a speck of dust that was captured. i have no clue what it is nor am i insinuating it is of alien nature. just strange and thought you might take a look.  file one is the first shot with nothing strange in it, file two is the second shot with the lights, file 3 is a crop of file 2. i have not altered the photos in any way other than to crop the second shot (3rd file). these are straight from the camera. these photos were taken with a cannon 6d with a 24-105 mm lens. if you have an opinion of what these may be, please email me with your thoughts. note, the file will say 2150. this is central time which is what my camera clock is set at. the actual time would be 2250 eastern time.
content.summary: Found these strange lights on my picture after i returned home. i did not notice anything while i was taking the picture

content.detailedDescription: I was driving east down route 724 and as i pulled up to a red light at the bethel church road intersection, i looked out my driver's side window and saw 4 bright white lights in the sky. they were in a straight line, but the line itself was at an angle, the line was at an almost diagonal angle, with the lower end being on the right hand side from my viewpoint. the traffic light turned green almost as soon as i saw the lights in the sky and i could not safely look out the window again. by the time i could-- maybe 30 seconds later, i no longer saw the object. i first thought the object was a low flying plane as there is a small airport nearby, but none of the lights were blinking and it was flying at a diagonal angle as opposed to horizontally, like most planes. the two passengers in the car (my parents) did not see the object but suggested it was a reflection in the window of something, but my window was down. they then suggested it was the lights from the nearby nuclear power plant, but those lights are blinking and were farther away than the lights i saw. i did not hear any noise associated with the lights. the lights seemed to fly similarly to an airplane but i did not get the best look. the lights were flying above the treetops, but not very far above. when i got home, i saw my boyfriend had texted me about the same lights and he happened to be in the same area at the same time i saw the lights. we both confirmed that we saw them at 8:43pm. he also said that he saw a different light in the sky get brighter and brighter and then it disappeared in the same area at about 8:45pm.
content.summary: 4 bright lights in a line

content.detailedDescription:
This is a story from someone who wishes to stay anonymous. i read this story and spent some time locating this person to try and obtain an interview.
after promising several times i would not tell who he was, he allowed me to interview him. this is a brief rundown of his story. the interview will follow.

i will try to cut most details out and get to the main story. it was 1988. i usually would be asleep by 8 p.M. nightly. i had to be at work by 5:30 a.M. every morning so i made sure to get my sleep. anyway. one night i was awoken by a bunch of dogs barking loudly.

i was very confused when i woke up because i wasn't in my bed. i was actually in the middle of my street walking. i found out the dogs were barking at me.

at this time i realized that i had no control of myself all i could move were my eyes. the next thing i remember was i was walking to this wooded bike trail area. i knelt down on one knee. with two hands on my bent knee i peeked threw some trees and bushes and saw a craft of some type. it was ball-shaped, no lights and landed under these huge power lines. i never saw the craft from the outside fly. as i looked at the craft an opening opened up and two smaller beings than me came out of the craft.

the next thing i remember was that i was boarding the craft. as i walked onto the craft the two beings followed me in the craft. the craft was kind of cramped and dark. it was dark but you could see like a neon kind of darkness. i then bent down and asked the being where we are going.

they answered me and said they are taking me behind the moon. i then asked why?

they said they couldn't be detected on earth’s radar from there. i said ok, then we took off. i looked out of some kind of window type thing and saw us leaving the earth. we passed the moon then made a u-turn type of turn back. this took less than 10 seconds. for some reason i wasn't scared at all.

i actually acted like i knew them. the next thing i recall was the only time i was really scared. i woke up again, this time naked in a funnel shaped pool filled with a greenish black gel type liquid. the pool had to be 20 yards wide all around. and pretty deep.

the pool was made of some kind of shiny metal. with the gel it made the surface very slippery and you would slip under the gel if you tried to get out. i then realized something very odd at that time. i wasn't alone.

there were at least 15 other humans with me. all of them screaming and panicking. this is what scared me. i didn't know what they were screaming about. i thought they knew something i didn't, so i got scared. some were under the gel moving around i could see. most were trying to escape.

one man kept climbing half way out. the closer he got to the top he would get hit by some sort of beam then he'd slid back into the pool. i thought this guy was insane, if he did get out where would he go? (i thought) i didn't see who was telling me but they where telling me not to be scared.

they told me i would be fine and that i could breath the gel. they said i could eat it and digest it. i couldn't drown in it. we could live in the gel. it also recycled human waste back into the gel.

i believed some of the humans were in the pool for years by the way they were acting. i figured a way to be under the gel and still breath air. that way they wouldn't hit me with the beam and make me slide under. i blacked out after that.

the next things i remember are some pretty vivid memories. i must let you know that i am deathly frightened of frogs. i know it sounds crazy but it's my one phobia. it's their skin. back to the story. i was rudely awaken by a being armpit high holding my hand taking me somewhere. i remember the touch of their hands it's woke me up from what ever i was under.

i tugged away and started to threaten them. i clinched my fist like i was going to fight. i said get away from me and if they touched me again i was going to hit them. he told me if i would do that i would change the world, as we know it. i knew if i hit them in the head my fist would go right threw them.

i didn't like the feel of their skin and i thought i sure wouldn't want its brains all over me.

so i was kind of stuck in defending myself or making a huge nasty mess all over me. that's when i realized that i was communicating to them with out my mouth. i knew what they were thinking and they knew what i was thinking.

it made things difficult for me at first. that's when the smaller beings brought over this taller being, a little taller than me. as the taller being approached me he told the smaller being that this is a (the) prophet. i looked at his face for maybe half a second. his face grossed me out so i never looked at him again.

if i looked at him again then he'd know how i felt about his appearance. i didn't want to offend him because i like this one he made me feel comfortable.

he explained that they wanted to do some medical examinations on me and if i would cooperated. i made a deal with him if they didn't touch me, hurt me or scare me then i would do it. he promised then i aloud them to do what they wanted. he also said he would answer all my questions that asked.

he walked me around as we talked. i looked at the ground the entire time so not to look at him. the next thing i remember was the medical examination.

first thing that i remember was coming out of a black out lying on a table. i was not scared what so ever. i trusted them.

and by being able to read their minds i know they weren't lying to me. as i remember they took some skin from my right arm. it was like the thinnest layer possible. unviable to my eyes, but all they needed.

next they took semen from me. i didn't understand this. again i wont go into to much details simply because this story would be about nine-hundred pages long.

i asked about this procedure later. the last thing they did to me was the strangest of all. they took my right eye out of my head. i actually saw the back of my eyeball and a cord or veins connected to it. i instantly ask about this.

next they put a babe like metal ball in my eye socket; about the size of a broken piece of rice. i asked, "what's that for?" they said so they can monitor me from space. i thought it was so they could see everything that i can see, like a video camera or something. then they put my eye back in then that was that?

my next memories were the taller being talking and i. this was the best part; because he answered my questions and showed me things in my head.

 
 
i don't know the exact order of my questions but i did ask away. i must inform you that they communicated to me like an adult would talk to a five-year-old child. with simple words; stuff like that. i thought it was funny.
anyway, the first question was about my semen. why? he told me so they can make baby humans in space. i simply said, "oh."

but then as i asked him questions he put visions in my head and showed me in an instant how they do it. as we were walking and talking about the humans in space he walked into this doorway that you can't even see until you look in it.

just as we were talking about humans in space these two kids about thirteen to fifteen years old one male one female turned to look at us. both human. full blooded perfect human beings.

they were both sitting down facing away from us. they turned around looked in my eyes. he sort of introduced us i guess. then they turned around and continued to do what they were doing.

believe it or not they were either controlling, driving or operating the craft or building were in. they were in control of operating something. i was tripping of this because they knew what they were doing and just little kids. they totally trusted them. crazy stuff.

and being that you can read minds in this situation i knew the kids won't scared or uncomfortable. they were programmed to master their job. there is much more to this topic also but that will scratch the surface of it. as we left i noticed he was taking me somewhere else.

this was kind of confusing to me also. this time it's like the room just appeared. we were just instantly in it. i think it's there doorways. they are unexplainable.

next thing i see is a dead cow hanging i believe head up butt down. nothing to my eyes was holding it up. i was baffled. i know cows can weigh tons but it was just hanging. next thing they did was dip it into some kind of gel in a box-shaped pool just big enough for the cow to fit in. strangely enough the gel didn't overflow when they put the cow in.

the pool was filled up. next they lifted the cow out and it was cut, dead and i was starting to get scared. i thought i was next. but then he showed me why they do this. it all related to the humans in space. he said what do humans eat as a child or infant.

i said milk. he said exactly. what do adult humans eat? i said hamburgers, steaks and food.

again he said exactly. then he put a vision again in my head and explained it all. they can't just take earth cows in space. they do just like they told me; he said we make our own cows in space. germ free no fleas no illnesses pure cows. just like the space humans perfect specimens.

like i said i have much more information on that topic also. then i asked about monitoring me behind my eye. they said humans do it all the time. he explained like this. how does a tiger explain to itself when it hears a helicopter coming out of the skies in the jungle? a big metal load scary object.

they all of a sudden they feel a pain in their hip and lose all control of everything except there eyes. then creatures come out of the object and start doing things to it. like tagging it's ear. like even taking teeth. they even take semen to preserve the species from extinction some times. basically scaring the crap out of the tiger for it's own good in a way.
content.summary: Abduction, telepathy, entity, encounter, ufo,

content.detailedDescription:
At 4:03pm on 4/22/2016 i was looking at the sky which was cloud free and deep blue with bright sunshine. i noticed a metallic object very far away which grabbed my attention. the object was definitely reflecting from the sun and it was relatively quick in the cycle of its reflective pattern. i continued to look at the object when 2 more were observed and they all shared the same characteristics. they were in a triangle type pattern but there was a great distance apart. they appeared to be traveling from the north heading southeasterly. intrigued by what i was seeing, i got 2 other co-workers to look at these objects.

as we all watched, i noticed another one following and this one appeared to be closer to me because its reflective qualities were far more evident. it followed the same type of flight path.   another two which appeared to possibly be attached came into view the same distance up as the first three. this group of orbs also had the same characteristics as the others but, the one underneath slowly went clockwise around the one it was traveling with and then came back down counterclockwise. i continued to watch all of them until such time as they were no longer visible to me. 

commercial airlines were in the sky and all of which left vapor trails behind. the objects didn't appear to be traveling very fast as i was trying to use the jets as basis for speed. it should also be noted that i was very close to new orleans international airport. 

i came home to do some searching online and came across a video where somebody in 2011 videoed the two orbs that look like they were connected in north america. according to the video, there were no other orbs in the area. 

i attempted to photograph what i was seeing, but there is nothing of evidentiary value on the picture.
content.summary: Multiple orbs having a metallic appearance and reflective nature to them but two others acted differently

content.detailedDescription:
I was going outside to get my dog from a corral we have in our backyard, as i was heading outside i had a flashlight (small) and my dogs leash. i had just passed one of my neighbors trees when i heard a sudden angry hiss come from it. this startled me and i originally thought it was a cat but there are only dogs in my neighborhood. (my cat was the last cat here before he passed away) i backed away from the tree and from the corner of my eye i saw movement, turning to my left which was facing se i saw a bright blue light rapidly climb into the air from it's position that i first saw it. then it came towards me, it was small so i knew i had some time to run back to my house. i turned around and started to shout/say "nope, nope. no way! i am going inside, nope!" mainly as a way to get myself to move faster and because this was the second time i witnessed the object. i didn't turn around because the moment you look back is when s*** goes down. i was scared and excited but mainly not wanting to deal with the object, i didn't want to have any confrontation with it and was more interested in heading back in.

my house is close to the corral, no more than maybe a distance of 30-50 feet away from the house. right next to the corral is a storeroom that has lights, a ceiling fan and flood lights on the outside. they use to be motion sensitive but were replaced with a simple switch to bring down the cost. after returning to the house i went to my parents room and informed my mother that the light was back. i had told her about the first time i had seen the light and hoped to show it to her. i figured it was safer if someone was with me than simply going back out there on my own. once back outside which took a while, mainly because she wanted to wait for a commercial break in her soap opera we were outside. this took about five to eight minutes at the most. outside the neighbors to my right, which was the area the light was coming from, were no longer outside. their lights were off and their blinds shut tight. i don't know but i think that they saw it coming as well.  

it is very note worthy for me to say that at the time of this incident and the previous one that my neighbors were outside with the lights on, then after i went back outside with my mother the lights were completely off. the first time i had seen it i did go back outside but by myself and noticed that the lights were promptly shut off and they were inside with the blinds closed. this is rather strange because they usually don't bother to close the blinds because we live out in the desert and no one bothers us. 

i know that the light is a craft, the origin i do not know. i have seen different crafts before this but none had ever come towards me and there was an incident when i was a child that makes me feel that there is more to the world than what we see everyday. i really hope that it doesn't come back but at the same time i want it to come back so i can take a picture or record it. for all i know this could be fine and nothing will happen to me.

content.detailedDescription:
Bright star very white with red "ears". noticed by 4 year old daughter. stationary for 6 minuets. i checked "sky map" app, no planet or star. after looking at sky map object had moved to lower location, maybe 1km further away in seconds. i took video with smart phone. no movement. item moved again, lower and maybe 1km further away, must have been instant. i videoed object and it instantly disappeared.
i was awiting for someone to return to the house, standing on the balcony with my daughter. she pointed out the "star" with the red on it.
i thought it was an airoplane, but no moving at all. i thought it could be a planet so went to get smart phone to check "sky map" app.
the object was still as i did all this 5 minutes. looked up to see the object had moved, took video but no event object was stationary. object had moved again. took video and the light just stopped.
not helicopter, object seemed too high and re-located too quick.Light was too bright and still. not plane it was stationary for long periods. 
had to be something we don't have here. hence took video
light stopped, stopped quicker than a bulb turned off.   

10deg 33 min n
103deg 28 min e

need help here with download video, will do if you are interested.

content.detailedDescription:
My sighting happened on the 25th november at around 3.30 am. i could not sleep due to the effects of the full moon, so i got up and thought ok since i cannot sleep i will go look to see if the full moon is out. i walked to the rear of our house to the back patio double doors. 

i saw the full moon bright and nicely nestled in-between our trees and fetched my husbands camera which i am not too familiar with but i opened the patio doors briefly to take some photos of the moon, it was cold. i was rather pleased with the photos as they turned out well. some would't focus because of the the light levels but some did. i do not know how to alter his cannon camera. 

i was just heading back to bed when i had an odd feeling, i thought i will just look once more at the beautiful full moon. as i did i saw an orange ufo appear from the east. for a second i watched it, then i thought, grab the camera. i turned it on and tried to focus it but it wouldn't focus as the light was too dim. all the time the craft was moving across the night sky. it appeared oval but it could have been saucer  shaped, the angle did not allow me to see if it were actually a saucer. it was travelling from the east to south west which would take it over lake erie. it was travelling at an angle about 40 to 45 degrees. it had a orange glow which gave it an outline and fuzzy lighter orange pulsating glow around it. i struggled with the camera as it would not pic up the ufo on the little screen. i decided to just aim and take photos in the hope it might catch something. i was really excited about the siting. while i followed the ufo i did try to remote view it and i did receive an image of the occupants, obviously as you know remote viewing is not an exact science as any real remote viewer would agree. i did however receive an image of a form of grey alien not with huge eyes but medium size eyes bigger in proportion than human eyes. these were tall and rather elegant aliens not the weak looking greys we normally see in the media. they were very intelligent and appeared to have some form of high collared gown or cape on.  they knew i was remote viewing them and told me they could not stop they were busy (on a schedule) i sent them a message of love and greetings to them, no fear at all. the ufo then disappear over my house and i moved to the front of the house but could no longer see it. 

on reviewing my photos i just caught an image by a fraction the bottom of the image is the refraction of my patio doors. i will attached the original and the one i blew up. i have not in any way altered the image just enlarged it. it is unfortunately not a wonderful photo and it really annoyed me i could not get the camera to focus and take a better photo or even film but at least i just managed to catch an image.  

i would like to add i am familiar with aircraft as i served in the royal air force as a aircraft mechanic propulsion (aircraft engines). so i am aware of weather balloons, helicopters, aircraft etc.. this was a ufo!
content.summary: Ufo looked oval but because it was travelling at about a 45 degree angle it may have been spherical, it pulsated but also still had a constant orange glow it slowly changed direction to flying towards lake erie

content.detailedDescription:
On or about april 29 2003 i was driving from dallas to mankato,mn.
staying off the toll roads and ended up on a road going around the south 
 of richard-gebaur afb, w markly rd. driving down an incline i saw 
a lake that was white capping in front of me due to a hurricane in the 
south. i made a left turn on the road and crossed a small 1 lane bridge
and looked to my left and saw a landed cigar shaped  craft about 25’
tall and unknown length since it was sitting in a canyon, i could only see 
three rows of 4 portals. i tried to stop because my video camera  was in the back seat. 
 a flock of turkeys were in front of me and 2 hit my windshield, not breaking it,
 i was going so slow. there were 2 farm houses with gates right up to road
 and couldn’t turn around.  got a couple of miles down the road and 
shrugged it of.  it’s been my head every day until now so i went to google 
earth and found it, and it was exactly how i remembered it, book marked it.
and went back 2 days later to look at it again and now the lake is gone, the farm
houses and it has been totally changed.
living in s.F. i can’t go back there to check it myself but it’s weird google 
earth changed.
james lambert
content.summary: Landed cigar shaped craft
